netaddradmin-2007
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

* Description

This is a simple management tool for local network addresses.  It can
reduce your cost to manage local IP addresses possibily assinged to
your network devices.  Host names and descriptions can be associated
with IP addresses.  List of host names can be output in the Unix
|/etc/hosts| format, which is useful for DNS-less network in
particular.  It also provides the "ping" view mode, which lists the
current status of availability of hosts using Unix |ping| command.

